high_descs: Turn around, then go straight toward the door, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the spoon on the counter, next to the knife.
Turn left, then go straight, then turn left to go to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Go to the cabinet, beneath the sink into the right.
Place the spoon in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around to your right, walk across the room and head to the counter beside the door
Pick up the spoon beside the knife on the counter
Turn to your left and head to the sink on your left
Place the spoon on the sink then rinse it
Pick up the spoon on the sink and find the cabinet under sink
Open the cabinet door and put the spoon inside right next to the salt
anns.task_desc: Put the clean spoon on the cabinet

high_descs: Turn around, head towards the white door, hang a left until you are facing the counter top.
Pick up the spoon with the black handle behind the knife on the counter top.
Turn left, cross the room until you reach the end of the counter on your right side, and hang a left to reach the sink.
Place the spoon in the sink on top of the knife to the left of the bottle, fill the sink with water before it reaches the top, and pick up the spoon from in the sink.
Turn around, cross the room towards the counter top, and turn back around to face the sink.
Open the lower cabinet door to the right of the sink, put the spoon inside the cabinet to the right of the salt shaker, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spoon inside a tall cabinet.
